    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_1087418244946576362.png",
                "id": "talent3347",
                "key": "Nightsun Style ",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Nightsun Style "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Select one of your characters, attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grapple Link</span> to self, and enter the <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span> state. Deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, then switch position with the selected character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Grapple Link</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the opposing side takes Burning DMG, or your other characters use a Technique:</span> The character to which this is attached gains 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul point</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When Nightsoul points are at 2:</span> Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grapple Prepare</span> to the character to which this is attached, then consume 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul points</span>. (After <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grapple Prepare</span> is attached, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">before your characters select their actions, if the attached character is the active character:</span> Deal 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG </span>to the nearest opponent)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(Rounds): 2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br>The character to which this is attached accumulates <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">\"Nightsoul points.\" </span>(Max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/c48d1d48d6a1dc63a64abf093de4fb1a_5031073248980634881.png",
                "id": "talent3805",
                "key": "Canopy Hunter: Riding High ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Canopy Hunter: Riding High "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span> and create 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Almighty Dragonlord, Ajaw</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/9cda2226c805b3b32e9d2136dd6f3b48_1807816575652221796.png",
                "id": "talent58223",
                "key": "Hail to the Almighty Dragonlord ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Hail to the Almighty Dragonlord "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, then deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span> to your opponent's next character.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1368050443105423284.png",
                "id": "talent56475",
                "key": "Almighty Dragonlord, Ajaw",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/fd18c308a948557901d1f3291df9535a_4098774257917253372.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Almighty Dragonlord, Ajaw"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_8547993821658619550.png",
                "id": "talent68890",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong><br>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> -1.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7807691410770727632.png",
                "id": "talent97764",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
