                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"I once undertook a commission to 'persuade a dangerous warrior.' When I found him, he happened to be playing this card game. I picked up a few tricks from watching him — enough to defeat him and walk away with my payment in full...\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Hint: Kinich's deck centers on using Techniques and is geared towards triggering Burning reactions. He can obtain many buffs by triggering Burning reactions and using Techniques.",
